Big Brother Nigeria 2018 housemate, Tobi has opened up on his salary while working at a popular national bank.  Some followers of the BBNaija show has in the time past accused the bank which is believed to play a big part in the reality show of sponsoring Tobi to the house but an allegation that has not been proven.  The 23-year-old Tobi revealed his salary while working and insisted he got bored of the job.  “I was earning 130k at the bank. At a point, I got bored doing the same thing every day. But my bosses were really nice to me. I was always being given gifts by my superiors,” he said. Do you have something awesome to share with the world? Click here to share Do you ever have any question about anything you wish to ask and get answer? Click here to ask Follow us on twitter @NigeriaTodayNG Also, Like us on facebook